id: act1_05_npc_encounter

prompt:
  Further along the path a young gardener kneels over an upset basket, fruit
  rolling toward the verge. They look up at you without quite asking for
  help.

choice c_help_gather:
  tendency: kindness
  text: Crouch down and gather the fruit back into the basket beside them.
  evidence: helped a stranger gather their spilled basket

choice c_offer_method:
  tendency: control
  text: Suggest a faster way to gather the fruit and demonstrate it.
  evidence: instructed a stranger on a faster way to do their work

choice c_walk_past:
  tendency: defiance
  text: Step over the fruit and keep walking; they didn't ask.
  evidence: walked past a stranger's spilled basket without helping
